default: using tacker with this model does not result in any detection/tracking
xy4x: uses threshold filtering with otsu algorithm and size of connected components
xy10x: uses the network trained on 17000 frames
xy10x_all: uses the network trained on 220000 frames for all 5 stages
xy10x_all_with_noise: uses the network trained on 220000 frames for all 5 stages, trained with noisy patterns added
